extendedInfo.description: If you take a photo of someone by this app, you can get  a photo of someone's forehead which has third eye. It is same as an eye of Mr. Tien who appeared in a famous comic.You can choose one of dialogues like "Kikoho!", "Dodonpa!", "Taiyoken!" and "I left xx."A photo will be stored in "tensan" folder.*Historyver.0.0.3- Fixed bugs.- Added error message for face detection.ver.0.0.2- Added linework.- Added balloon and dialogue.
